          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Two isotopically enriched 96Zr samples in chemical",
                " form of ZrO2 powder were used.",
                " A gold sample (15mm diam. x  1mm thick, 3.423 g) was",
                " used as a standard for neutron capture cross section",
